    "body": "Try it in a browser, or any js console:\r\n```\r\n> 9999999999999999000\r\n10000000000000000000\r\n```\r\nJavascript is quirky that way. You should use `BigNumber` to handle large numbers with accuracy. \r\nExample:\r\n```\r\n> new BigNumber(\"9999999999999999000\")\r\n9999999999999999000\r\n\r\n```",
